      "span_text": "Control or transfected cultures were exposed to 125 nM BoNT/A for 2 h at 37 • C, before being assayed for SV recycling with monoclonal antibodies directed against the intravesicular domain of synaptotagmin I (Syt-ecto Abs; clone 604.2, kind gift of Dr. R. Jahn, Gottingen) as previously described [CITATION_2] ."
